comments: Kennard (LAC) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage with one another as the entry pass into the post is made.
Coffey (LAC) is moving forward when marginal body contact occurs with Jokic's (DEN) back as Jokic is passing.
Reed (DEN) brings his left arm toward Bledsoe's (LAC) path and marginal contact occurs with Bledsoe's front as Reed attempts to defend over the pick.
Zubac (LAC) firms up in his screening position in Reed's (DEN) path and absorbs the contact, some of which occurs to Reed's leg.
Kennard (LAC) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Reed (DEN) briefly has his arm around Zubac's (LAC) upper half before quickly removing it.
Reed (DEN) contests the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Kennard (LAC) during the follow-through.
Jokic (DEN) and Kennard (LAC) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.

Mann (LAC) maintains verticality as incidental arm contact occurs with Jokic's (DEN) left arm in the post. After the initial contact, Mann is moving slightly forward when marginal body contact occurs as Jokic is passing.
Bledsoe (LAC) cleanly dislodges the ball away from Reed (DEN) before any incidental contact occurs.
As Reed (DEN) falls to the floor following the dislodge, incidental foot-to-foot contact occurs with Coffey (LAC) in the lane.
Barton (DEN) extends and initiates body contact with Bledsoe (LAC) in transition.
Morris (DEN) engages and disengages with Kennard (LAC) as they move over the screen.
Ibaka (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Reed's (DEN) path and absorbs the contact.
Bledsoe (LAC) moves toward Jokic's (DEN) path and marginal body contact occurs at the end of Bledsoe's drive.
Jokic (DEN) jumps toward Bledsoe (LAC) and marginal body contact occurs with Bledsoe's extended left leg as he is passing.
Barton (DEN) contests the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Coffey's (LAC) left arm after the release.
Jokic (DEN) brings his arm up when marginal contact occurs with Mann (LAC) as Mann retrieves the rebound and attempts the subsequent put-back.
Rivers (DEN) sets the pick on Mann (LAC) and does not deliver the contact as the defensive switch takes place.
Jokic (DEN) rolls toward the post after the expiration of the pick and incidental contact occurs with Kennard (LAC) as Kennard goes under.
Ibaka (LAC) firms up in his screening position in Rivers' (DEN) path and absorbs the contact.
Rivers (DEN) brushes Mann's (LAC) left arm and marginal contact occurs at the end of Mann's drive.
Mann (LAC) overtly and abruptly veers into Jokic (DEN), and delivers contact to Jokic during his upward shooting motion.
Mann (LAC) is bringing his arm into a vertical position and absorbs the arm contact that occurs as Morris (DEN) is passing.
Bledsoe (LAC) cleanly intercepts the pass intended for Jokic (DEN).
Jokic (DEN) jumps alongside Bledsoe's (LAC) path when marginal body contact occurs during Bledsoe's layup attempt.
Mann (LAC) and Jokic (DEN) come together at the same spot in the lane and marginal contact occurs to Jokic's side during rebounding.
Jokic (DEN) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Kennard (LAC) brings his off-arm toward Morris' (DEN) front and marginal contact occurs as Kennard releases away toward the sideline.
Morris (DEN) legally contests Kennard's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Kennard (LAC) and Johnson (LAC) each move toward Barton (DEN) and marginal contact occurs with Barton's body and left arm as he splits the double team.
Mann (LAC) commits a take foul on Barton (DEN).
Bledsoe (LAC) initiates contact across Jokic's (DEN) side and left arm as he receives the inbound. This contact occurs prior to Bledsoe making contact with the ball.
Reed (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Boston Jr. (LAC) along the perimeter.
Jokic (DEN) is in the lane for less than three seconds when Boston Jr. (LAC) loses control of the ball at 0:03.9 and is in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent thereafter.
Reed (DEN) retreats away from Boston Jr. (LAC) and legally contests the jump shot attempt as Boston Jr. jumps forward toward him.
